Magingo aya, Igikomangoma Harry n’umugore we Meghan ntibakibarizwa mu bafite inshingano mu muryango w’ibwami, aho biyemeje kubaho mu buzima bwabo nk’abantu basanzwe muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika.
Ni umwanzuro bafashe ku giti cyabo, ku mpamvu zirimo ko Meghan atari yishimiye ubuzima yari abayemo nk’umunyacyubahiro w’ibwami.
Guhitamo umwanzuro nk’uyu hari ibintu byinshi bemeye guhara, birimo kuba bahabwa ubutumwa n’umwamikazi bakajya kumuhagararira hirya no hino no kuba batazongera kugenerwa amafaranga bahabwaga kubera inshingano bari bafite.
